      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * CSVN</b>\n</p><p><b>CSVN</b> - Computer Schaak Vereniging Nederland, the Dutch Computer Chess Federation.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History_of_the_CSVN\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History of the CSVN</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Tournaments\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tournaments</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Computerschaak\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Computerschaak</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Board_of_the_CSVN\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Board of the CSVN</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2012\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2012</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2018\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2018</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History_of_the_CSVN\">History of the CSVN</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CSVN&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: History of the CSVN\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>The <b>CSVN</b> was founded in <a href=\"/Timeline#1980\" title=\"Timeline\">1980</a> by ...\n</p>\n<table>\n\n<tr>\n<td>  <div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/Max_Euwe\" title=\"Max Euwe\"><img alt=\"MaxEuwe.jpg\" src=\"/images/5/59/MaxEuwe.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"250\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div>\n</td>\n<td>  <div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/Jan_Louwman\" title=\"Jan Louwman\"><img alt=\"JanLouwman.jpg\" src=\"/images/8/82/JanLouwman.jpg\" width=\"198\" height=\"250\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div>\n</td>\n<td>  <div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/Jaap_van_Oosterwijk_Bruyn\" title=\"Jaap van Oosterwijk Bruyn\"><img alt=\"OosterwijkBruyn.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/OosterwijkBruyn.jpg/173px-OosterwijkBruyn.jpg\" width=\"173\" height=\"260\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/OosterwijkBruyn.jpg/260px-OosterwijkBruyn.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/OosterwijkBruyn.jpg/346px-OosterwijkBruyn.jpg 2x\" /></a></div>\n</td>\n<td>  <div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\"><img alt=\"VanDenHerik.jpg\" src=\"/images/8/89/VanDenHerik.jpg\" width=\"145\" height=\"250\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Max_Euwe\" title=\"Max Euwe\">Max Euwe</a>\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Jan_Louwman\" title=\"Jan Louwman\">Jan Louwman</a>\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Jaap_van_Oosterwijk_Bruyn\" title=\"Jaap van Oosterwijk Bruyn\">Jaap van Oosterwijk Bruyn</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>\n</td></tr></table>\n<p>... and others <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> . First chairman was <a href=\"/Jaap_van_Oosterwijk_Bruyn\" title=\"Jaap van Oosterwijk Bruyn\">Jaap van Oosterwijk Bruyn</a>.\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tournaments\">Tournaments</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CSVN&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Tournaments\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>The <b>CSVN</b> yearly organizes the\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Dutch_Open_Computer_Chess_Championship\" title=\"Dutch Open Computer Chess Championship\">Dutch Open Computer Chess Championship</a> from <a href=\"/DOCCC_1981\" title=\"DOCCC 1981\">1981</a> to <a href=\"/DOCCC_2011\" title=\"DOCCC 2011\">2011</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> , see <a href=\"/Jan_Louwman#FirstDutchChampionship\" title=\"Jan Louwman\">Jan Louwman's announcement</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/International_CSVN_Tournament\" title=\"International CSVN Tournament\">International CSVN Tournament</a> from <a href=\"/ICT_2001\" title=\"ICT 2001\">2001</a> to <a href=\"/ICT_2013\" title=\"ICT 2013\">2013</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/CSVN_Programmers_Tournament\" title=\"CSVN Programmers Tournament\">CSVN Programmers Tournament</a> since <a href=\"/PT_45\" title=\"PT 45\">2013</a></li></ul>\n<p>as well as users tournaments with <a href=\"/Dedicated_Chess_Computers\" title=\"Dedicated Chess Computers\">dedicated units</a>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Computerschaak\">Computerschaak</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CSVN&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Computerschaak\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>The <b>CSVN</b> regularly publishes the <a href=\"/Computerschaak\" title=\"Computerschaak\">Computerschaak Journal</a>, two issues a year. Editor is <a href=\"/Hans_van_der_Zijden\" title=\"Hans van der Zijden\">Hans van der Zijden</a>, who in October 2010 superseded <a href=\"/Eric_van_Reem\" title=\"Eric van Reem\">Eric van Reem</a>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Board_of_the_CSVN\">Board of the CSVN</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CSVN&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Board of the CSVN\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010\">2010</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CSVN&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The board of the CSVN in 2010:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Cock_de_Gorter\" title=\"Cock de Gorter\">Cock de Gorter</a> Chairman</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Kees_Sio&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Kees Sio (page does not exist)\">Kees Sio</a> Treasurer</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ries_van_Leeuwen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ries van Leeuwen (page does not exist)\">Ries van Leeuwen</a> Member administration</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Rienk_Doetjes&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Rienk Doetjes (page does not exist)\">Rienk Doetjes</a> Secretary</li></ul>\n<p>Non board functions:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Hans_van_der_Zijden\" title=\"Hans van der Zijden\">Hans van der Zijden</a> Editor Computerschaak</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jan_Krabbenbos\" title=\"Jan Krabbenbos\">Jan Krabbenbos</a> Webmaster</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2012\">2012</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CSVN&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2012\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The board of the CSVN from December 1st, 2012:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Jan_Krabbenbos\" title=\"Jan Krabbenbos\">Jan Krabbenbos</a> Chairman</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Geert_Roelof_van_der_Ploeg&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Geert Roelof van der Ploeg (page does not exist)\">Geert Roelof van der Ploeg</a> Treasurer and member administration</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Richard_Pijl\" title=\"Richard Pijl\">Richard Pijl</a> Secretary</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ruud_Martin\" title=\"Ruud Martin\">Ruud Martin</a> Member</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hans_Secelle\" title=\"Hans Secelle\">Hans Secelle</a> Member</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Marcel_van_Kervinck\" title=\"Marcel van Kervinck\">Marcel van Kervinck</a> Member</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2018\">2018</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CSVN&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2018\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Ruud_Martin\" title=\"Ruud Martin\">Ruud Martin</a> Chairman</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jan_Krabbenbos\" title=\"Jan Krabbenbos\">Jan Krabbenbos</a> Temporary Treasurer</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Folkert_van_Heusden\" title=\"Folkert van Heusden\">Folkert van Heusden</a> Secretary</li></ul>\n<p>Non board functions:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Hans_van_der_Zijden\" title=\"Hans van der Zijden\">Hans van der Zijden</a> Editor Computerschaak</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jan_Krabbenbos\" title=\"Jan Krabbenbos\">Jan Krabbenbos</a> Webmaster</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CSVN&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=3896\">An Open Letter to Cock de Gorter and the CSVN Board</a> by <a href=\"/Harvey_Williamson\" title=\"Harvey Williamson\">Harvey Williamson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Hiarcs Forum</a>, December 28, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40151\">Rybka to play in Leiden?</a> by <a href=\"/Graham_Banks\" title=\"Graham Banks\">Graham Banks</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 23, 2011 <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40489\">Fwd: Open letter to the CSVN</a> by <a href=\"/Marcel_van_Kervinck\" title=\"Marcel van Kervinck\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 21, 2011, on behalf of <a href=\"/Amir_Ban\" title=\"Amir Ban\">Amir Ban</a>, <a href=\"/Don_Dailey\" title=\"Don Dailey\">Don Dailey</a>, <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt</a>, <a href=\"/Gerd_Isenberg\" title=\"Gerd Isenberg\">Gerd Isenberg</a>, <a href=\"/Marcel_van_Kervinck\" title=\"Marcel van Kervinck\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen\" title=\"Stefan Meyer-Kahlen\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a>, <a href=\"/Fabien_Letouzey\" title=\"Fabien Letouzey\">Fabien Letouzey</a>, <a href=\"/Thomas_Mayer\" title=\"Thomas Mayer\">Thomas Mayer</a>, <a href=\"/Daniel_Mehrmann\" title=\"Daniel Mehrmann\">Daniel Mehrmann</a>, <a href=\"/Gian-Carlo_Pascutto\" title=\"Gian-Carlo Pascutto\">Gian-Carlo Pascutto</a>, <a href=\"/Richard_Pijl\" title=\"Richard Pijl\">Richard Pijl</a>, <a href=\"/Ralf_Sch%C3%A4fer\" title=\"Ralf Schäfer\">Ralf Schäfer</a>, <a href=\"/Mark_Uniacke\" title=\"Mark Uniacke\">Mark Uniacke</a>, <a href=\"/Ben-Hur_Carlos_Vieira_Langoni_Junior\" title=\"Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Junior\">Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Júnior</a>, <a href=\"/Harvey_Williamson\" title=\"Harvey Williamson\">Harvey Williamson</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/ICGA_Investigations#CSVN\" title=\"ICGA Investigations\">ICGA Investigations - Aftermath</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://rybkaforum.net/cgi-bin/rybkaforum/topic_show.pl?tid=23052\">Computer chess on a suicide mission</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Rebel</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Rybka Forum</a>, September 22, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://rybkaforum.net/cgi-bin/rybkaforum/topic_show.pl?tid=23125\">An idea to save the CSVN tournament</a> by <a href=\"/Jeroen_Noomen\" title=\"Jeroen Noomen\">Jeroen</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Rybka Forum</a>, September 30, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=428635&amp;t=40709\">Re: how far is too far: houdini for sell?</a> by <a href=\"/Marcel_van_Kervinck\" title=\"Marcel van Kervinck\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 12, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47963\">Open letter to chess programmers</a> by <a href=\"/Richard_Pijl\" title=\"Richard Pijl\">Richard Pijl</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 11, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49432\">CSVN Autumn Tournament</a> by <a href=\"/Richard_Pijl\" title=\"Richard Pijl\">Richard Pijl</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 23, 2013</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CSVN&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csvn.nl/\">CSVN Computerschaak Home</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/\">Old CSVN Site</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csvnsupplementsite.nl/\">CSVN Supplement Site</a> (Dutch)</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csvnsupplementsite.nl/webpagesall.html\">Alle pagina's Computerschaken, Schaken</a></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CSVN&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Frans_Morsch\" title=\"Frans Morsch\">Frans Morsch</a> and <a href=\"/Jaap_van_Oosterwijk_Bruyn\" title=\"Jaap van Oosterwijk Bruyn\">Van Oosterwijk Bruyn</a>, <a href=\"/DOCCC_1986\" title=\"DOCCC 1986\">DOCCC 1986</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csvnsupplementsite.nl/CSVNPAGINA3.html\">Computerschaak pagina 3</a> (Dutch)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csvnsupplementsite.nl/CSVNPAGINA1.html\">Computerschaak pagina 1</a> (Dutch) Redactie: J. ten Have and Drs. S. Kooi</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csvnsupplementsite.nl/csvnp2.html\">CSVNP2.html - Eerste Nederlands Kampioenschappen Computerschaken. De CSVN periode van oprichtingsdatum (18 oktober 1980) tot eind 1981. Het begin. Nederlandse kampioenschappen vanaf 1982</a> (Dutch)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerschaak.nl/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=514%3Arybka-en-de-icga&amp;catid=18%3Avereniging&amp;Itemid=28&amp;lang=en\">Rybka and the ICGA</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228220223\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.023 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.027 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 99/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 190/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:1939-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228220223 and revision id 7841\n -->\n"
